# quoted-string-adjacent-escapes

## Input

```
a "\\\\"
b "\n\t"
c "\\\""

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..27
  ENTRY@0..9
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    QUOTED_STRING@2..8
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@2..3 "\""
      STRING@3..7 "\\\\\\\\"
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@7..8 "\""
    NEWLINE@8..9 "\n"
  ENTRY@9..18
    WORD_KEY@9..10
      WORD@9..10 "b"
    SPACE@10..11 " "
    QUOTED_STRING@11..17
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@11..12 "\""
      STRING@12..16 "\\n\\t"
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@16..17 "\""
    NEWLINE@17..18 "\n"
  ENTRY@18..27
    WORD_KEY@18..19
      WORD@18..19 "c"
    SPACE@19..20 " "
    QUOTED_STRING@20..26
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@20..21 "\""
      STRING@21..25 "\\\\\\\""
      DOUBLE_QUOTE@25..26 "\""
    NEWLINE@26..27 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: QuotedString {
                open_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@2..3 "\"",
                string: STRING@3..7 "\\\\\\\\",
                close_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@2..3 "\"",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@9..10 "b",
            },
            value: QuotedString {
                open_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@11..12 "\"",
                string: STRING@12..16 "\\n\\t",
                close_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@11..12 "\"",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@18..19 "c",
            },
            value: QuotedString {
                open_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@20..21 "\"",
                string: STRING@21..25 "\\\\\\\"",
                close_quote: DOUBLE_QUOTE@20..21 "\"",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

